{
  "stem": "2170.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was only with my brother and a couple boys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to do it so much and so fast.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were German soldiers shot also because Russian planes start to come in and bomb, tried to bomb one or two.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The station and German soldiers fell dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So SS, there was a lot SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they took me to, to put them into a grave.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were, maybe-- this was a good job, actually, for every German soldier to dig a second-- there was maybe 50 of them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As soon we finished to digging the graves, the Germans told us to get out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they put them into the graves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They made speeches.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So this was already action.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Once the-- from the Judenrat, one of the policemen grabbed me for work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he told me, the Germans need somebody-- because the Germans start to come in already.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because the Russian Army, the Red Army, was attacking and attacking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They came closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were armies from all over-- Italian, Spanish, together with the Germans, fighting like brothers-- Axis.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this Jewish policeman says to me that I have to go to work to German spot over there in Zhmerinka.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I went with another couple boys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "As we came to a couple of buildings there near the station, a railroad station, the German came in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were with trucks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they said-- they show about 10 buildings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we have to paint this up very soon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "If you're not going to finish the job, they-- he took out the gun.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He's going to shoot us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it was cold at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They gave us paint, and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I saw that I will never do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And German trucks already coming in.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
